'''Biter''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]], [[Season 2|second]] and [[Season 4|fourth]] seasons. He is played by [[Gerard Jordan]] and debuts in &quot;[[The Night Lands]],&quot; though he was also portrayed by an unidentified extra in &quot;[[Fire and Blood]]&quot;. Biter is a menacing criminal forcibly recruited into the [[Night's Watch]].

